SQL_STMT_U.val: select distinct a.groupid,o.user_code ,o.u_name,a.MODID,b.PUBNAME,b.DESCRIPTION,coalesce(f_add,0) tambah,coalesce(f_update,0) edit,coalesce(f_delete,0) hapus,coalesce(f_print,1) cetak from ousr o ,SYS_MENUGRP a left join SYS_MENU b on b.MNID=a.MNID left join SYS_MNACCESS c on c.PUBLIC_NAME=b.PUBNAME and PRIV_ID=a.groupid where o.Locked='N' and a.GROUPID=o.DfltsGroup and b.PUBNAME<>'' order by user_code,MODID,PUBNAME
